<statement>
<p>
In the simple interest formula <m>\displaystyle{I}={P}{r}{t}</m>, what unit must <m>\displaystyle{t}</m> be given in?</p>
<p><ol style="list-style-type:upper-alpha"><li>Quarters</li> 
<li>Decimals</li> 
<li>Weeks</li> 
<li>Years</li> 
<li>Months</li> 
<li>Days</li> 
<li>Whatever unit is given in the problem</li> 
<li>There is no particular unit</li> 
</ol></p>


</statement>
<answer>
<p><ul><li>D: Years</li></ul></p>
</answer>

